description:
&lt;p&gt;Band 5/6 Operating Department Practitioner ODP &lt;br /&gt; &lt;br /&gt; Are you that person? It takes a certain kind of person to be a good Operating Department Practitioner, someone who can think on their toes, work both independently and as part of a team, and plan ahead for their patients’ needs. &lt;br /&gt; We are looking for Qualified ODP to work within our friendly hospital environment, to support and assist our ENT; Rhinology, Laryngology &amp; Otology clinicians. It is essential that you are reliable, punctual and work well within a team environment, and hold the National Certificate or equivalent.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Are you an ODP looking to develop your skills in one of the largest and most successful Foundation Trusts in the UK?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;UCLH have a reputation as a centre of clinical excellence&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Based in the busy West End of London, they have a lively and vibrant working atmosphere, with quick and easy transport links to all the sites&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;They have new facilities and state-of-the-art medical technology&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop your skill within Anaesthetics, Scrub or Recovery gaining experience in one of the UK’s most prestigious hospitals&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;UCLH can offer a rare opportunity to work as a Theatres Nurse within Neurosurgery&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our Bank Nurses are invaluable to us and in return for their dedication and commitment, we offer the following benefits:-&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;The opportunity to work across all UCLH departments gaining invaluable skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Access to “Lines of Work” (guaranteed short, medium or long term shifts)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Specialist pay rates&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Self service electronic timesheet submission, with weekly pay&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A designated onsite co-ordinator to offer support and introduce you to various departments within UCLH&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A dedicated recruitment team to ensure you can work as quickly as possible&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A bookings team to ensure you work when and wherever you want to&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you are looking to further your career in a hospital that has cutting edge technology, and you have atleast 6 months NHS experience please apply online.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
